data.description: Welcome to your new home in Madison Heights! Step into this charming ranch home and feel the warmth envelop you. With 3 bedrooms and 1 bath all on the same level, this  layout offers space to gather in its open living design. Imagine the possibilities as you explore the potential for a finished half bathroom in the basement, perfect for adding convenience and value to your home. Need a place to work or unwind? Look no further than the finished basement area, ideal for a home office or a home entertainment room. The living room is filled with brightness and warmth, offering a doorwall that leads to your fully fenced backyard—a private sanctuary just waiting for your personal touch. This space offers the possibility of enjoying lazy afternoons or hosting gatherings with space available for a paver patio or deck, and the option to keep a small above ground pool for those sunny days. Your kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting gas range cooking, plenty of natural light, and space for delightful eat-in dining experiences. From morning coffees to gourmet dinners, a kitchen is where memories are made. This home is located in close proximity to both 696 and I 75 giving convenient access to downtown Detroit and the surrounding Metro Detroit area. New residents of this home can also enjoy the discounted rate at nearby Red Oaks Water Park and have easy access to their favorite stores in the surrounding area. The seller is offering the new owners a home warranty. Schedule your showing today and make this house your home or a add a new investment property to your portfolio!
